# 🛒 Blinkit Checkout Billing Calculator

A simple **Blinkit-inspired Checkout Billing Calculator** built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**. This project demonstrates fundamental JavaScript concepts such as **var, let, const, template literals, object destructuring, DOM manipulation, user input handling, and console methods** while recreating a modern grocery checkout experience.

---

## 📌 Project Overview

This project simulates the checkout page of Blinkit, where users can:

* View a preloaded shopping cart
* Enter delivery details
* Apply coupon discounts
* Add delivery partner tips
* Choose a payment method
* Generate a complete billing summary

The application automatically calculates all charges and displays a professional-looking order summary.

---

## ✨ Features

* 🛒 Preloaded Blinkit shopping cart
* 👤 Customer information form
* 📍 Delivery address input
* 🎟️ Coupon code selection
* 💰 Tip for delivery partner
* 💳 Multiple payment methods
* 🧾 Automatic bill generation
* 🚚 Delivery fee calculation
* 📦 Handling charges
* 🛍️ Small cart fee (when applicable)
* 🧮 Automatic GST calculation
* 📊 Console logging using `console.log()` and `console.table()`
* ⏱️ Execution time measurement using `console.time()`
* 🎉 Success notification after bill generation
* 📱 Responsive and modern Blinkit-inspired UI

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript (ES6)

